  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Commission to Study Reparation Proposals for African-Americans Act</title>
    <title type="display">Commission to Study Reparation Proposals for African-Americans Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">To acknowledge the fundamental injustice, cruelty, brutality, and inhumanity of slavery in the United States and the 13 American colonies between 1619 and 1865 and to establish a commission to examine the institution of slavery, subsequently de jure and de facto racial and economic discrimination against African-Americans, and the impact of these forces on living African-Americans, to make recommendations to the Congress on appropriate remedies, and for other purposes.</title>
  </titles>
